    ApproverClaimsListActivity
    Activity that allows a user to look at all the different submitted claims Not finished

    Activity to allow the approver to look at the different expenses of a submitted claim
    ClaimantClaimsListActivity
    The activity that the claimant will come to if they have already logged in.
    ClaimantExpenseListActivity
    Activity where a user can see the overview of their claim including all of their expenses.

    LoginActivity
    Activity that user will see upon first starting app, prompts for login and saves username for next session
    TagManagerActivity
    Activity where a user can view a list of their tags and also edit, delete, or add new tags
